Package: pearsonCorrelateCells
Type: Package
Title: A package to identify correlated cells based on the target expression
  pattern
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Wing Chung Jessie", "Lam", 
                  email = "jessiewingchung.lam@mail.utoronto.ca", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Wing Chung Jessie Lam <jessiewingchung.lam@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: pearsonCorrelateCells takes the top genes in a 
  single or set of RNA-seqencing clusters, or in bulk RNA seqencing 
  data, and carry out Pearson correlations of genes with each spot in 10X 
  visium spatial transcriptomic data to identify the similar cells.
